{"type":"text","timestamp":1775895008407,"sessionID":"ses_2846b0c2affeHerQ03pZ9MkRHy","part":{"id":"prt_d7b972235001TTmyma9X58JDX1","messageID":"msg_d7b96fafc001z2QXs7WSX3k5Fd","sessionID":"ses_2846b0c2affeHerQ03pZ9MkRHy","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-037 PCAP Analyzer Example\n\n### SDK Python (sdk-python/)\n\n| Requirement | Status |\n|------------|--------|\n| Package layout matches spec | ⚠️ Partial |\n| `pyproject.toml` exists | ✅ |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` exports | ✅ `CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` exports | ✅ All 3 client classes |\n| No single `Configuration` class | ✅ Distributed defaults |\n| Timeout defaults (120s, 5.0s connect) | ✅ |\n| Pool settings (10, 10) | ✅ |\n| `examples/basic_usage.py` | ❌ Missing |\n| `scripts/e2e_picod_test.py` | ❌ Missing |\n| SDK tests passing | ✅ **120 passed** |\n\n### PCAP Analyzer Example (example/pcap-analyzer/)\n\n| Requirement | Status |\n|------------|--------|\n| `main.py` CLI with typer | ✅ |\n| `analyzer.py` core logic | ✅ Uses `CodeInterpreterClient` |\n| `parsers/` directory | ✅ TCP, HTTP, DNS parsers |\n| `utils/` directory | ✅ file_utils, report_utils |\n| `exceptions.py` | ✅ Custom exception hierarchy |\n| `README.md` documentation | ✅ |\n| `tests/` directory | ❌ Empty - **no tests** |\n| `sample_data/` directory | ❌ Empty - no test PCAP files |\n| `pyproject.toml` for packaging | ❌ Missing - not installable |\n| **Critical: `types.py` naming** | ❌ **Shadows Python stdlib `types` module** - causes circular import failure |\n\n### Critical Issues Found\n\n1. **`types.py` naming conflict**: File `example/pcap-analyzer/types.py` shadows Python's standard `types` module, causing circular import failures. Should be renamed to `models.py` or `data_types.py`.\n\n2. **Missing tests**: PCAP analyzer `tests/` directory is empty.\n\n3. **Not installable**: Missing `pyproject.toml` or `setup.py` for the example package.\n\n4. **Missing SDK examples**: `basic_usage.py` and `e2e_picod_test.py` per spec.\n\n### Summary\n\n**SDK Core**: ✅ Implemented correctly, 120 tests passing\n**PCAP Example**: ❌ Critical bugs prevent usage - needs `types.py` renamed, tests added, and packaging setup","time":{"start":1775895008405,"end":1775895008405}}}
